data.description: The best value for this fantastic location! Just down the street and over the bridge is the coveted Anna Maria Island. Less than 5 miles away to the NW is Robinson Preserve and to the east, Bradenton River Walk which offers you sunset strolls as well as pubs, live music, and a plethora of fabulous dining options. Nearby private school options include CES Academy, Saint Steven's Episcopal School, and world-renowned IMG Academy. The home is nestled in a dead-end street with a split floor plan that presents TWO primary suites. One en-suite primary bedroom is positioned across the hall from two bedrooms that utilize a separate full bath. The other primary en-suite bedroom offers the option of utilizing a private entrance, providing ideal space for a tenant or guest. The heart of the home features a large kitchen graced with granite countertops and an abundance of cabinet space. The breakfast bar allows for guests and littles to spend time with you as you prepare simple snacks or settle into the eat-in kitchen table for a heart-filled meal. After dinner, cozy up on the couch for a movie in the step-down family room or relax in the living room near the wood-burning fireplace. Feeling like s'mores by the fire or backyard games? Enjoy the platform deck and the security of the fenced lawn. Roof is 2022 and AC is 2015.
